Showing one ad per screen (Google)
Clearly distinguish ads from content
Ad content rating matches referring app content rating
KIDOZ is one of Google Play’s certified ad networks
Every campaign & ad creative is checked manually by our in-house team
All ad campaigns are reviewed manually for relevance, appropriateness and compliance
All ad campaigns are checked manually to ensure that they do not collect any personal information, such as name, date of birth, email address, location, etc.
Campaigns are displayed in most relevant apps
Developers working with Kidoz are required to mark the content targeting of their apps when adding them to Kidoz dashboard.
Kidoz editorial team then manually checks each app and compares the age rating with that shown in Google Play and AppStore to target only appropriate ads for a certain age (e.g. 5 and under)
Ad campaigns are displayed in apps that are most relevant, based on age, gender and content, to ensure suitability and successful delivery
